# Architecture

```
src/
  app/(auth)/          login, register, reset-password
  app/(protected)/     dashboard, orders, quotes, contact (middleware-gated)
  app/api/             server routes for orders, quotes, custom orders
  components/          UI building blocks
  lib/supabase/        client, server, middleware helpers
  lib/constants.ts     regions, service types, HSSS contacts
  types/               Builder, Order, Quote, OrderStatus
supabase/migrations/   versioned SQL
```

- Orders persist in Supabase before any email work.
- `builders.user_id` links to `auth.users.id`. RLS scopes all builder data.
- Next.js App Router only — no legacy Vite stack in this repo.
